**Overview**

This dashboard provides an overview of the bot and DoS related activities detected by the F5 BIG-IP.

The dashboard is designed to offer comprehensive statistics and display the ingested logs related to bot and DoS activities from F5 BIG-IP.

It shows a breakdown of events by severity, action and OS name. The dashboard presents the distribution of bot and DoS events over time. Additionally, it includes the top 10 source IP and destination IP of bot and DoS. Furthermore, it illustrates detailed information about the detected events and their respective data models.
